<p><strong>Ambrose London Prix Fixe</strong><br />
安布羅斯餐廳倫敦店的套餐菜單<br />
<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/ambrose-london-prix-fixe">http://www.scp-wiki.net/ambrose-london-prix-fixe</a><br />
作者：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600571135" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;">stormbreath</a></span><br />
