為第七屆年度<a href="/art-exchange-hub">藝術交換</a>而寫，給 <span class="error-inline"><em>FloppyPhoenix</em> does not match any existing user name</span> 的禮物，FloppyPhoenix 請求一些關於異常食物的場景。</p>
